                <note rend="inline" type="source">550.S1/770: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Great Britain</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Atherton</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-05-12T20:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 12, 1933—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>108. For Norman Davis. Your 121, May 12, 9 p.m. This is a splendid job. You have
                    my best congratulations.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
